   -----------------------------------------------------------------
    Applies to Windows client only with release earlier than 1.0.7
   -----------------------------------------------------------------
  
   To upgrade from a client version 1.0.6 or earlier release, rename
   the files 

	.nessus.keys  to  nessus-keys.cfg

   and 
        .nessusrc     to  nessusrc.cfg

   Note that the file finder may not be aware of these files unless
   you turn the "show all files" on in your Windows Explorer, somtimes
   accessed (depending on your system language) as

        View -> View -> Hidden files: () show all files
